      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRUTH TELLER (3) started big odds last time but hit the ground running with a strong early split, giving a sight but fading only late to finish third (19.57) at Healesville over 350m. The form out of last race has been strong. Can go on with it. FROG MARCH (4) turned in a moderate performance last time when fifth at this track over 390m behind Sharapova Star (22.41) in a Grade 4. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Shapes as one to consider. MR. KIA ORA (7) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (22.88) in a Grade 5 H at Warrnambool. Solid record at the distance winning 12 races. The form from his last run stacks up well. Likely to play a prominent role. KALUNA CHAOS (6) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
